\begin_layout Itemize
Then 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{2}^{I}=\beta^{I}\left(\theta\right)$
\end_inset

.
 The 2 groups value public money differently.
 
\begin_inset VSpace medskip
\end_inset


