 industries.
 Reported income 
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{ij}^{R}$
\end_inset

 relates to true income through 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{ij}^{True}=\begin{cases}
Y_{ij}^{R} & \text{if }i\text{ is wage worker}\\
\lambda_{j}Y_{ij}^{R} & \text{if }i\text{ is self-employed}
\end{cases}
\]

