\begin_layout Itemize
Use comprehensive household expenditure data from 31 countries to document
 patterns of informal (untaxed/untaxable!) consumption, summarized in the
 
\emph on
informality Engel Curve
\emph default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Descriptive findings suggest consumption taxes are strikingly progressive
 (contrary to consensus view)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Plug these moments into a simple optimal tax framework
