\emph on
level
\emph default
 is higher
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{\hat{c}-c}/\varepsilon_{y}$
\end_inset

 is higher: Evasion decisions relatively more responsive than production
 decisions.
