\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\pi}$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\tau_{\pi}\left(y-c\right)=\tau_{y}y\text{ \ \ }\Leftrightarrow\text{ \ \ }\hat{\pi}\equiv\frac{y-c}{y}=\frac{\tau_{y}}{\tau_{\pi}}.
